### ================================================================
### Product Service - Gateway 경유 외부 API 테스트
###
### 사전 조건:
###   1. docker-compose 로 인프라 (PostgreSQL, Gateway, Keycloak, Eureka) 실행
###   2. docker-compose 로 Company / Product 서비스 실행
###   3. company-crud.http [1] 실행 → companyId 글로벌 변수 확보
###   4. 환경 드롭다운에서 'gateway' 선택
###   5. keycloak-auth.http 실행 → accessToken 확보
###
### 흐름:
### Client
###  → Gateway (JWT 검증 + Header 주입)
###    → ProductService
###
### Gateway 책임:
### - JWT 검증
### - X-User-Id, X-User-Role 자동 주입
### ================================================================


### ================================================================
### [1] 상품 생성 (MASTER)
### ================================================================
### @name createProduct
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "companyId": "{{companyId}}",
  "hubId": "{{hubId}}",
  "name": "Gateway 테스트 상품",
  "price": 10000,
  "stock": 100
}

> {%
    client.test("상품 생성 성공", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 201);
        client.assert(response.body.data.id !== undefined, "productId 반환 필요");
    });
    // 성공(201)인 경우에만 저장 — 실패 시 data가 undefined라 TypeError 방지
    if (response.status === 201 && response.body.data) {
        client.global.set("productId", response.body.data.id);
    }
%}


### ================================================================
### [2] 상품 단건 조회
### ================================================================
### @name getProduct
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
    client.test("상품 단건 조회 성공", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200);
        client.assert(response.body.data.id === client.global.get("productId"));
    });
%}


### ================================================================
### [3] 상품 목록 조회 (전체)
### ================================================================
### @name getProducts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
    client.test("상품 목록 조회 성공", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200);
    });
%}


### ================================================================
### [4] 상품 목록 조회 (이름 검색)
### ================================================================
### @name searchProducts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products?name=Gateway
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
    client.test("상품 이름 검색 성공", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200);
    });
%}


### ================================================================
### [5] 상품 수정 (이름/가격 변경)
### ================================================================
### @name updateProduct
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Gateway 수정 상품명",
  "price": 20000
}

> {%
    client.test("상품 수정 성공", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200);
        client.assert(response.body.data.name === "Gateway 수정 상품명");
    });
%}


### ================================================================
### [6] 재고 수정 (MASTER)
### ================================================================
### @name updateStock
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}/stock
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "stock": 200
}

> {%
    client.test("재고 수정 성공", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200);
    });
%}


### ================================================================
### [7] 상품 삭제
### - product_stock 도 함께 soft delete 처리됨
### ================================================================
### @name deleteProduct
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
    client.test("상품 삭제 성공", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 200);
    });
%}


### ================================================================
### 오류 케이스
### ================================================================

### [8] 인증 토큰 없이 요청 → 401 expected
### @name unauthorizedRequest
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products

> {%
    client.test("인증 실패 (401)", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 401);
    });
%}


### [9] 존재하지 않는 상품 조회 → 404 expected
### @name notFoundProduct
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/products/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000099
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

> {%
    client.test("상품 없음 (404)", function () {
        client.assert(response.status === 404);
    });
%}